gov.nih.nci.hl7.clone.meta
Class HL7V3MetaObjectParser

java.lang.Object
  gov.nih.nci.hl7.clone.meta.HL7V3MetaObjectParser

public class HL7V3MetaObjectParser
extends java.lang.Object

Parse HL7 v3 Meta Object into caAdapter HL7 v3 specification object. There are two modes to create the HL7 v3 specification object: maximum and minimum mode. The H3S file should be created using minimum mode. Default is minumum mode.

Since:
caAdapter v1.2
Version:
$Revision: 1.1 $
Author:
OWNER: Eric Chen Date: Jun 3, 2005, LAST UPDATE: $Author: marwahah $
